# PocketBase: track schema (pb_migrations) + hooks + dev runner; ignore
# runtime state, the downloaded binary, and vendored docs. The `/*` + `!`
# idiom keeps everything ignored by default and opts only source back in, so
# pb_data (a prod copy: user data, password hashes, secrets) can't be added.
/pocketbase/*
!/pocketbase/pb_migrations/
!/pocketbase/pb_hooks/
!/pocketbase/serve.sh
/pocketbase/pb_data/
/icons

# Claude Code
bugs/
reviews/
